The walksheds.geojson must follow this pattern:

{
  "type": "FeatureCollection",
  "features": [
    {
      "type": "Feature",
      "properties": {
        "station_id": "A01",
        "station_name": "Metro Center",
        "minutes": 5
      },
      "geometry": {
        "type": "Polygon",
        "coordinates": [...]
      }
    }
  ]
}
Required properties:

station_id → WMATA station code (string)
minutes → integer (5, 10, 15, 20)
